 [ 1 swap times [ i 1+ * ] ] is !     ( n --> n )

 [ dup 2 < iff
     [ drop false ] done
   dup 1 - ! 1+
   swap mod 0 = ]            is prime ( n --> b )

  [] 3000 times
    [ i^ 2 *
    dup 1 - prime iff
      [ dup 3 + prime iff
        [ dup 5 + prime iff
          join else drop ]
      else drop ]
    else drop ]
  echo
